{"tid":522070,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"反抗，為了留下一根火苗","createTime":"2018-01-07T08:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T02:04:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5e906e6599e4a021982961c205bc6cd67a72866f","tid":522070,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T08:07:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%8D%E6%8A%97-%E7%82%BA%E4%BA%86%E7%95%99%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%80%E6%A0%B9%E7%81%AB%E8%8B%97/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%258A%2597-%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BA%2586%25E7%2595%2599%25E4%25B8%258B%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E7%2581%25AB%25E8%258B%2597%2F&d=9T5muvOEbKPxekxzFkzEdgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=6b4e6a23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%258A%2597-%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BA%2586%25E7%2595%2599%25E4%25B8%258B%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E7%2581%25AB%25E8%258B%2597%2F&h=c06f2bc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%8D%E6%8A%97-%E7%82%BA%E4%BA%86%E7%95%99%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%80%E6%A0%B9%E7%81%AB%E8%8B%97/</a><br />\n<br />\n反抗，為了留下一根火苗<br />\n<br />\n2018/1/4 &mdash; 19:11<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/sing_PByh8_1200x0.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fsing_PByh8_1200x0.PNG&h=9dd60977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《星球大戰》宣傳照<br />\n<br />\n剛剛偷懶，看 Star Wars 去也。<br />\n<br />\nThe Resistance 面對比自己強大一千幾百倍的 First Order，被追殺得只死剩幾百個。社會上，少數權貴樂於在 First Order 下壓搾大眾來發達，而被壓搾的千千萬萬人卻又不敢出聲，這種局勢下，the Resistance 能夠頂住 First Order 而重新建立民主共和國的機會，幾乎是零，但他們還是要撐下去，為的，就是戲中反覆提到的 spark，即火苗。<br />\n<br />\n只要還有一根火苗留下，就算這一代人成功不了，下一兩代人在前人的基礎上，還大可成功，畢竟，星星之火可以燎原。但若果火苗熄滅了，後代就只得迷失在在黑暗中，重頭摸索，不知要犧牲多少代人的幸福才有機會成功，難了。<br />\n<br />\n這，就是當代人拚命的理由。少年時代讀過的《銀河英雄傳說》，說的，就是這根火苗。<br />\n<br />\n為什麼香港還是有那麼多人明知鬥不過還是堅持下去? 沒別的，也是為了保存這一根的火苗。<br />\n<br />\np.s. Star Wars 裡頭實在蘊藏了西方的宗教哲學兼歷史，有空再聊。<br />\n<br />\n（標題為編輯所擬；原刊於作者 facebook）"},{"pid":"c33dac436899cc4e5a2b9826d42b786f20ec5098","tid":522070,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T02:04:04.000Z","msg":"Star Wars 係真係革命軍架<br />\n<br />\n你泛民點反抗呀? 新假期紮營呀？<br />\n<br />\n天行者紮營反黑帝, 你都唔會入場睇啦<br />\n<br />\nON<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}